    # --- CGA 8x8 high half (CP437 0x80..0xFF) — added in 0.5.1 (ADR 0007).
    # 128 glyphs sourced byte-for-byte from Linux's lib/fonts/font_8x8.c
    # (public-domain IBM CGA 8x8). The ASCII half above is the AGNOS hand-
    # drawn original, so this font now mixes two PD sources: the box-
    # drawing range (0xB0..0xDF) is geometric and style-neutral; the
    # accented-letter glyphs (0x80..0xAF, 0xE0..0xFF) may not perfectly
    # match the hand-drawn aesthetic, but having coverage beats a blank
    # high-half. Mechanically generated; fidelity spot-checked in tests.
